@DATABASE "Orion"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - O - Orion"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - O
                   ====================================

                                   Orion
                                   =====



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Immunity " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(37319,201)"}               37319,201
@{"Lives = x" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(38059,255)"}               38059,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

@endnode
